   "endLine": 312,
   "source": "<ROUTINE HAT-F (\"AUX\" TEMP)\n\t <COND (<VERB? EXAMINE LOOK-ON READ>\n\t\t<SAY-THE ,HAT>\n\t\t<TELL \" is decorated with foil stars and cheap glitter.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? LOOK-INSIDE LOOK-DOWN>\n\t\t<COND (<DONT-HAVE? ,HAT>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)>\n\t\t<FCLEAR ,HAT ,RMUNGBIT>\n\t\t<TELL \"Weird! It's like peering into an endless well.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<AND <VERB? TAKE>\n\t\t     <IN? ,HAT ,PELICAN>>\n\t\t<SAY-THE ,PELICAN>\n\t\t<TELL \" would rather you didn't.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? WEAR>\n\t\t<TOO-LARGE ,HAT T>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<AND <VERB? PUT THROW>\n\t\t     <EQUAL? ,PRSI ,HAT>>\n\t\t<COND (<DONT-HAVE? ,HAT>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (<EQUAL? ,PRSO ,HAT>\n\t\t       <WHAT-A-CONCEPT>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (<EQUAL? ,PRSO ,HANDS>\n\t\t       <TELL \"You feel \" D ,HANDS \" tingling.\" CR>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)>\n\t\t<SET TEMP <GETP ,PRSO ,P?SIZE>>\n\t\t<COND (<G? .TEMP 5>\n\t\t       <TOO-LARGE ,PRSO>)\n\t\t      (<FSET? ,HAT ,RMUNGBIT>\n\t\t       <TELL\n\"Maybe you should look inside the \" D ,HAT \" first.\" CR>)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <SAY-SURE>\n\t\t       <TELL \"put \">\n\t\t       <ARTICLE ,PRSO T>\n\t\t       <TELL D ,PRSO \" into the \" D ,HAT \"?\">\n\t\t       <COND (<YES?>\n\t\t\t      <SET TEMP <+ .TEMP <GETP ,DCASE ,P?CAPACITY>>>\n\t\t\t      <PUTP ,DCASE ,P?CAPACITY .TEMP>\n\t\t\t      <MOVE ,PRSO ,DCASE>\n\t\t              <SAY-THE ,PRSO>\n\t\t\t      <TELL \" disappears into the \" D ,HAT>\n\t\t\t      <NO-TRACE>)\n\t\t\t      \n\t\t\t     (T\n\t\t\t      <TELL ,OKAY \"you're still holding \">\n\t\t\t      <ARTICLE ,PRSO T>\n\t\t\t      <TELL D ,PRSO \".\" CR>)>)>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? REACH-IN>\n\t\t<PERFORM ,V?PUT ,HANDS ,HAT>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>>"
