   "source": "<ROUTINE PRINCESS-F (\"OPTIONAL\" (CONTEXT <>))\n\t <THIS-IS-IT ,PRINCESS>\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,VESTIBULE>\n\t\t<TAKE-MIND-OFF ,PRINCESS>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,TORTURE-CHAMBER>\n\t\t<COND (<VERB? TAKE PUSH MOVE>\n\t\t       <COND (,CLAMPED?\n\t\t\t      <STILL-CLAMPED>)\n\t\t\t     (T\n\t\t\t      <TELL D ,PRINCESS\n\" probably wouldn't enjoy being manhandled.\" CR>)>)\n\t\t      (<ASKING? ,PRINCESS>\n\t\t       <COND (,COAT-WORN?\n\t\t\t      <NO-TALKING>)\n\t\t\t     (T\n\t\t\t      <HAD-TIME \"questions\">)>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)\n\t\t      (<VERB? TELL REPLY HELLO WAVE-AT ; GOODBYE>\n\t\t       <COND (,COAT-WORN?\n\t\t\t      <NO-TALKING>)\n\t\t\t     (T\n\t\t\t      <HAD-TIME \"conversation\">)>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)\n\t\t      (<VERB? RESCUE UNLOCK RELEASE>\n\t\t       <HOW?>)\n\t\t      (<OR <HURT? ,PRINCESS>\n\t\t\t   <VERB? YELL KISS RUB SQUEEZE>>\n\t\t       <PRINTD ,PRINCESS>\n\t\t       <MIGHT-NOT-LIKE>)\n\t\t      (<AND <VERB? GIVE>\n\t\t\t    <EQUAL? ,PRSI ,PRINCESS>>\n\t\t       <COND (,COAT-WORN?\n\t\t\t      <NO-TALKING>)\n\t\t\t     (T\n\t\t\t      <TELL D ,PRINCESS\n\" gracefully declines your offer.\" CR>)>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (<PRINCESS-SPECIFIC?>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <RFALSE>)>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<CROWD-F>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>>"
