   "endLine": 203,
   "source": "<ROUTINE WAKE-BABY (\"OPTIONAL\" REASON)\n\t <TELL \"Oh, no! \">\n\t <COND (.REASON\n\t\t<TELL .REASON>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL \"Your reckless fumbling\">)>\n\t <TELL \" woke up the \" D ,BABY \"!|\n|\nThe little creature \">\n\t <COND (,LIT\n\t\t<TELL \"blinks helplessly in the glow of\">\n\t        <CANDLE-OR-STONE>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL \"gurgles angrily in the \" D ,DARKNESS>)>\n\t <TELL \".\">\n\t <MOTHER-COMES>>"
